videos.headline: Duke fumble recovery sets up Blue Devils in red zone
videos.description: Andy Davidson run for 5 yds to the Army 9 Andy Davidson fumbled, forced by Corbin McCarthy, recovered by Duke Dylan Singleton

videos.headline: P. Boehme 3-yard TD pass to E. Schneider
videos.description: Parker Boehme pass complete to Erich Schneider for 3 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Army recovers fumble after delivering booming hit
videos.description: Army's Rhyan England throws his body directly into Duke QB Daniel Jones which forces him to let go of the ball and subsequently be recovered by Army.

videos.headline: Duke stuffs Army on 4th and 1
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw run for a loss of 6 yards to the Army 32

videos.headline: D. Jones 22-yard TD pass to A. Young
videos.description: Daniel Jones pass complete to Aaron Young for 22 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Army blocks punt to set up offense in Duke territory
videos.description: Austin Parker punt blocked by Jaylon McClinton blocked by Jaylon McClinton

videos.headline: Duke makes another 4th down stop to prevent Army from scoring
videos.description: John Trainor run for a loss of 5 yards to the Duke 9

videos.headline: A. Davidson 45-yard TD run
videos.description: Andy Davidson run for 45 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Duke stops Army again on 4th down
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw run for no gain to the 50 yard line

videos.headline: A. Davidson fights off defenders with stiff arm during 39-yard run
videos.description: Andy Davidson run for 39 yds to the Army 44 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Duke defender flips Army runner with hit
videos.description: Duke's Breon Border sniffs out the Army run play and hits the Black Knights' John Trainor when he gets the ball, causing Trainor to flip to the ground for a 3-yard loss.

videos.headline: Duke recovers fumble with Army driving
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw run for no gain to the Duke 31 Ahmad Bradshaw fumbled, recovered by Duke Alonzo Saxton II

videos.headline: Duke intercepts pass late in 4th Quarter
videos.description: Ahmad Bradshaw pass intercepted Deondre Singleton return for no gain to the Duke 41
